{"tid":1562954,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"各位記住 \"非禮零容忍\" 如果有人嗌非禮 一定要幫手制服","createTime":"2019-09-12T08:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:24:31.000Z","uid":111637,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"212d2a515d7e92d2a2d785fa65ee6110a591f9d8","tid":1562954,"uid":111637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"我係隔離開post　撞飛咗拍片阿叔嘅樓主<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1562667/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1562667/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n依個post想分享第二個經歷。。。<br />\n<br />\n有次喺地鐵站入面<br />\n見到有個阿叔 係咁擋住一個女學生嘅去路<br />\n又係話咩要畀錢呀盛呀<br />\n睇落有啲唔對勁<br />\n<br />\n擾攘咗一陣<br />\n個女學生大叫一聲：非禮呀！<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n跟住 在旁潛伏已久嘅幾名壯漢(包括我)<br />\n立即上前制服住個阿叔！！！<br />\n<br />\n幾對結實爆青筋嘅手臂 同時衝前㩒住個猥瑣阿叔 <br />\n㩒到佢腰都彎埋<br />\n<br />\n個阿叔一直畀啲爭扎　<br />\n一直叫我地做曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哼！你有見過咁大力嘅曱甴咩？？！！！<br />\n<br />\n就喺我地制服阿叔嘅時候 個女學生跑走咗。。。<br />\n唉 可能佢覺得羞愧啦<br />\n各位記得一定要勇於出聲 先可以杜絕非禮架！<br />\n<br />\n但當刻 既然個女學生都選擇唔追究喇<br />\n我地幾個壯漢唯有放手 鬆開個阿叔<br />\n<br />\n個阿叔條腰 有少少伸唔翻直<br />\n佢彎住腰手指指 好勞氣咁問候我地娘親<br />\n我地就雙手舉起表示無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐　有啲職員行過黎了解<br />\n我地堅稱只係以為有罪惡發生<br />\n幫手捉住非禮嘅嫌疑犯<br />\n係見義勇為嘅表現！！<br />\n係良好市民應負嘅責任！！！<br />\n<br />\n個阿叔雖然睇落好心生不忿<br />\n最後亦只能用一場誤會作解釋散場<br />\n<br />\n睇住個阿叔扶住條腰 guk下guk下咁遠去嘅背影。。。<br />\n<br />\n我心中無悔！！！<br />\n如果再遇到有女性。。。或者男性啦<br />\n大嗌非禮嘅時候　我一樣會企出黎幫手捉嫌疑犯！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正所謂：「遠火call消防，近火嗌非禮！」<br />\n我地一眾手瓜起展嘅兄弟　一定會幫你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f949c530215b512fd64a97bde8293dc900e17c9d","tid":1562954,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c6b6c707ee9c717e38ab1cda8149f418af41ed98","tid":1562954,"uid":100371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41c91078960c5c63e3366b0383b8bd66e3e4a98","tid":1562954,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"依個推，請所有女士有咩事大叫非禮，手足會出手"},{"pid":"dab4caed439a3aab967383175d02ac72da344c58","tid":1562954,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"【狂賀】發放Fake news策略非常成功,連登子女功不可沒!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558530</a>"},{"pid":"e9c023e99548b0eed93b8cbbb3079a1ae4532934","tid":1562954,"uid":195124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e71886e5d1cecfbe4cc7d0f7f93236812de36e","tid":1562954,"uid":276393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor